org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class liquidfun.b2DistanceJoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.liquidfun.b2Joint
        • org.bytedeco.javacpp.liquidfun.b2DistanceJoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    liquidfun

    @NoOffset
public static class liquidfun.b2DistanceJoint
extends liquidfun.b2Joint
    A distance joint constrains two points on two bodies to remain at a fixed distance from each other. You can view this as a massless, rigid rod.
